For a cloud:

5 Essential characters:
- on demand services: (No human interaction)
-Broad n/w access: Allows to connect in any way(mobile, laptop,etc)
-Resource pooling: (The range of maxm services they can provide, we require huge hardware and software)
-Rapid Elasticity: if i increase my load from 2 to 200 , i should get offered. Scale up and Scale down.
-Measured service : pay as per usage
-Multi Tenacity

